@23   = ~This amulet has a dull, unimpressive chain attached to a fist-sized steel pendant. On the pendant is the engraving of two hands bound together by a red cord - the only actual color on the amulet.~
@24   = ~Being most truthful and powerfull servant Dar gained this amulet from his goddess Ilmater as a reward for his deads. The Holy Symbol has a dull, unimpressive chain attached to a fist-sized steel pendant. On the pendant is the engraving of two hands bound together by a red cord - the only actual color on the amulet. When worn, the symbol empowers the Painbearer with Ilmater‘s power.

STATISTICS:

Armour Class Bonus: +2
Strength Bonus: +1
Wisdom Bonus: +1
Magic Resistance: +15%

Vocalize
Decrease Spell Casting Speed by 2
Grants two additional 6th and 7th level spells

Protection from Evil
Complete Mind Shield
  (Immunity to any mind-alterating effects and psionics).~
