@177  = ~Translocation Arrows~
@178  = ~These potentially dangerous arrows are exceedingly rare, typically only appearing as individual items.  As weapons, they are abysmally poor.  As strategic tools, they are quite useful.  These arrows were frequently used by melee fighters with competent bow skills.  Once they had fired off their Translocation Arrow, they could enter melee and finish a protected target at close range.

