@179  = ~Bone Cleaver Axe~
@180  = ~The handaxe or throwing axe is also known as a hatchet. The axe blade has a sharp steel tip, counterbalanced by a pointed fluke. The short handle has a point on the bottom and the head may have a spike on the top. Besides its superb craftsmanship, tiny runes of power can be seen etched all along the surface. It‘s obvious a lot of time and effort went into its creation and although not apparent at first, a slight reddish glow can be seen emanating from the runes.

