Usable by:
 Cleric
 Druid
 Monk~
@422  = ~Moth Ridden Thistledown~
@423  = ~This used to be a very fine quality, grayish material before the moths began to eat through it. Thistledown is a high prized material from which cloaks of elvenkind are fashioned. It is very light and does not snag easily on branches.  Due to its high quality, the elves had very little trouble enchanting it.~
