@766  = ~Vashon‘s Key~
@767  = ~This unique looking key is Vashon’s personal key. You can tell this because in very fine print along one side is a message: "Personal property of Vashon. If you are a student, congratulations! Step one complete. If you are a thief, congratulations! Disintegrate spell commencing now..."~
@768  = ~Ezekiel~
@769  = ~Kalinor‘s Body~
@770  = ~Flurried voice~
@771  = ~Staff of Besieging~
@772  = ~A favorite among transmuters, this particular staff was created by a wizard named Gulph the Tiny. A diminutive human mage, Gulph didn‘t want to be stuck in a situation where he would have to rely on his physical abilities. This staff helped him have the upper hand in magical duels. Gulph met his end when he foolishly went looking for Ibenian Mushrooms in a grove full of quicklings. The staff remained among the quicklings for several years until a passing party of adventurers slaughtered the evil fae creatures and took the staff as their own.

Combat Ability:
