@773  = ~Cario De‘Vince~
@774  = ~Coordinator~
@775  = ~Tilorn's Wardstone~
@776  = ~The symbol carved into this weighty, granite wardstone is difficult to discern. It almost appears to flicker, as if continuously altering its silver-inlaid shape.~
@777  = ~Eurich's Wardstone~
@778  = ~The symbol carved into this granite wardstone may something to do with detection of time portals. As suggested by Eurich, you may try and use this wardstone on any portal you discover in your travels.~
@779  = ~Arvilais~
@780  = ~Dhailan~
