@1188 = ~Kheros the Red wore this blood-red suit of plate mail through many of the years that he fought for the church of Tempus.  He was born as the son of humble farmers near Calaunt.  When he was a young man, he set off for the city to hire himself out as a mercenary.  After a number of successful endeavors, Kheros became a short-term member of many adventuring companies.  Along the way, despite his many victories, Kheros became disgusted and terrified by the sight of blood.

